| type.title_04 | The font used for smallest-level headings, such as breadcrumb links and page navigation | Title 4 font |
| type.body_01 | The font for body text | Body type font |
| type.small_01 | The for the smallest body text used | Small type font |
| type.font_size.title_01 | The font size for top-level headings | Title 1 font szie |
| type.font_size.title_02 | The font size for secondary headings | Title 2 font szie |
| type.font_size.title_03 | The font size for minor-level headings | Title 3 font szie |
| type.font_size.title_04 | The font size for smallest-level headings | Title 4 font szie |
| type.font_size.body_01 | The font size for body text | Body type font size |
| type.font_size.small_01 | The font size for small body text | Small type font size |
| type.line_height.title_01 | The line height for top-level headings | Title 1 line height |
| type.line_height.title_02 | The line height for secondary-level headings | Title 2 line height |
| type.line_height.title_03 | The line height for minor-level headings | Title 3 line height |
| type.line_height.title_04 | The line height for smallest-level headings | Title 4 line height |
| type.line_height.body_01 | The line height for body text | Body type line height |
| type.line_height.small_01 | The line height for small text | Small type line height |

#### Page element and image dimension properties

| Property | Description | Studio Field |
| ---------| ----------- | ------------ |
| size.pixel.spacing_slim |The smallest amount of space between related elements | Slim spacing (pixels) |
| size.pixel.spacing_medium | The tertiary-level of space between related elements | Medium spacing (pixels) |
| size.pixel.spacing_wide | The second-largest level of space between related elements | Wide spacing (pixels) |
| size.pixel.spacing_xwide | The largest level of space between related elements | Extra Wide spacing (pixels) |
| size.pixel.input_h | The height of input boxes and buttons | Input Box / Button height (pixels) |
| size.pixel.icon_mini | The size of the smallest icons | Mini icon size (pixels) |
| size.pixel.icon_small | The size of small icons | Small icon size (pixels) |
| size.pixel.icon_medium | The size of medium-sized icons | Medium icon size (pixels) |
| size.pixel.avatar_message_w | The maximum width of avatar images used in messages | Max. Avatar width (Message (px)) |
| size.pixel.avatar_message_h | The maximum height of avatar images used in messages | Max. Avatar height (Message (px)) |
| size.pixel.avatar_profile_w | The maximum width of avatar images used in the user profile | Max. Avatar width (Profile (px)) |
| size.pixel.avatar_profile_h | The maximum height of avatar images used in the user profile | Max. Avatar height (Profile (px)) |
| size.pixel.avatar_inline_w | The maximum width of avatar images used in-line | Max. Avatar width (Inline (px)) |
| size.pixel.avatar_inline_h | The maximum height of avatar images used in-line | Max. Avatar height (Inline (px)) |
| size.page_width_min | The minimum page width in pixels. The browser will not resize smaller than this setting | Minimum page width |
| size.page_width_max | The maximum page width in pixels or percentage. If pixels is specified, the minimum page width is ignored and the page is set at the maximum width specified here. | Maximum page width |


